Colobaspis is a genus of beetles in the family Megalopodidae, containing the following species:

Colobaspis aeneipennis Weise, 1915
Colobaspis atrithorax Pic, 1934
Colobaspis bicolor Papp, 1952
Colobaspis bicoloriceps Pic, 1922
Colobaspis carinata Bryant, 1930
Colobaspis costatipennis Pic, 1937
Colobaspis dollmani Bryant, 1930
Colobaspis elegans Chujo, 1951
Colobaspis femorata Gressitt, 1942
Colobaspis flavonigra Fairmaire, 1894
Colobaspis fraxini Komiya, 1986
Colobaspis hargreavesi Bryant, 1930
Colobaspis kwangtungensis Gressitt, 1942
Colobaspis lacordairei Westwood, 1864
Colobaspis neavei Bryant, 1930
Colobaspis notaticollis Pic, 1952
Colobaspis nyassae Bryant, 1930
Colobaspis omeiensis Gressitt, 1942
Colobaspis pallida Gressitt, 1942
Colobaspis pulchra Baly, 1859
Colobaspis regalis Achard, 1920
Colobaspis septemmaculata Hope, 1831
Colobaspis speciosa Baly, 1859
Colobaspis suturalis Clavareau, 1909
Colobaspis theresae Pic, 1947
Colobaspis vitalisi Pic, 1922